DO you know the latest fashion in town, when it comes to ladies’ dress (gown, skirt and top)? If you have been following the fashion trend, you would have noticed that the latest ladies’ dress in vogue is the floral looks. And it is getting hotter by day. The floral dress is the fashion must-have this season. Believe it; it is for ladies of class and fashion. Beautiful and stylish floral prints are in vogue. They are remarkably apparent this season and add a subtle and sexy appeal to one’s look. Floral print comes in different patterns and designs, depending on the style. Go for prints that complement your frame. Styling tips